values:
I want to have my genes spliced with those of an electric eel. I'll call myself "the electric heel." I will live in both the land and the sea and if you make me mad you'll get shocked. And I don't mean shocked by my rude behaviour, which you may well be, I mean shocked by energy coming through your god damn face.

Hoo-boy, I sure am stir crazy. Let's get guns.
